{"tid":694231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"水警冒雨跪一哥求原諒　涉「死亡拍賣」遭停職","createTime":"2018-06-08T07:11:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T13:33:45.000Z","uid":54373,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0836b05eb6b59fe99873d911e8dc4c93ee85fc1e","tid":694231,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T07:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180608/photo/bkn-20180608124941019-0608_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180608134333\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180608%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180608124941019-0608_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180608134333&h=7660bec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水警今午在警總西面閘跪在地上，求警隊一哥原諒。(讀者提供)<br />\n<br />\n灣仔警察總部出現警員冒雨跪地奇景。一名水警今日(8日)中午在警總西面閘跪在地上，求警隊一哥原諒。據悉，跪地水警姓鄭，駐守水警北分區，現正被停職。 <br />\n<br />\n消息指，有人涉嫌於15年派發單張，稱可在自己的宿舍舉行「死亡拍賣直擊活動」，單張註明以拍賣方式，價高者得，在其油塘油美苑宿舍進行自殺，如跳樓、燒炭、吊頸、割脈等活動，並歡迎傳媒拍攝，拍賣所得金錢歸於其妻及兒子。"},{"pid":"2fa4392bfd3153451faa949e37f377691363611c","tid":694231,"uid":137248,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T07:14:30.000Z","msg":"屌你咁多痴線佬做警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d592d824a81f59ec432463b290d4f89c6516f1","tid":694231,"uid":65743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T07:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/08/151521_7a488534562b6c1e41696c99d5da7b05.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F08%2F151521_7a488534562b6c1e41696c99d5da7b05.gif&h=43d19980&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bf27701fd83fde89a9d27079379c1ef33e669e4","tid":694231,"uid":4420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T07:15:52.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"352928